  %p open to all developers in the Kitty Pad family. The monthly service will be obtained as In-app purchases through any app partnered with KittyPad and allow access to all apps in the KittyPad umbrella.

%div{"data-role"=>"collapsible", "data-collapsed"=>"false", "data-theme"=>"a"}
