  %p users will choose your games because they have more to offer than just fun, but a promise of health protection.

%div{"data-role"=>"collapsible", "data-collapsed"=>"false", "data-theme"=>"a"}
  %h3 Exchange Download
  %p cross promotion across other apps in the KittyPad SDK or just across your portfolio-you choose. Targeted users intuitively see links to your applications and can be linked to ITunes to download.

%div{"data-role"=>"collapsible", "data-collapsed"=>"false", "data-theme"=>"a"}
